OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland first to ban      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fanaesthetic over           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fenvironment                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland has become the first country  
OL,6, in the world to stop its hospitals     
OL,7, using the anaesthetic desflurane       
OL,8, because of the threat it poses to the  
OL,9, environment.                           
OL,11,FNHS data suggests the gas, used to keep
OL,12,Fpeople unconscious during surgery, has 
OL,13,Fa global warming potential 2,500 times 
OL,14,Fgreater than carbon dioxide.           
OL,16,FBanning it in Scotland - from its peak 
OL,17,Fuse in 2017 - would cut emissions equal
OL,18,Fto powering 1,700 homes a year.        
OL,20,FUK hospitals have already cut down.    
